{
  "stem": "18281.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 150.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Another interesting part of the Reichmann family-- I don't know if that's of interest to you-- is that when the Germans marched in, and they being Hungarian subjects, even though they were religious Jews, the Germans didn't touch them because they were not Austrians.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when the Reichmanns eventually immigrated to Paris and they had to fill out a form.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How much money they took with them-- and they were quite wealthy even then.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Reichmann marked on the paper, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't figure that one out, playing dumb.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was called Otto-- O-T-T-O, Otto Bondy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was born in 1897.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Vienna.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He, he was kind of a trombenik, if you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was all-- he was a, a joker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He always had a laughing face.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I recall he always was good for a practical joke.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember him smearing somebody that had a, a sunburn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He told them that rubbing sand on it would help him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have to tell you that this didn't help very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember that once my uncle fell asleep on the street car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when they came to their own stop, he told the fellow, let them sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And by the time my uncle woke up, he was three miles down the road.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Those are the kind of practical jokes that he played.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that he was under the Italian front, that they had-- while he was not hurt, he certainly told me that they had a lot of hardships, tremendous cold-- those winters in the mountains on, on the Italian front.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't have much to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that whatever wasn't nailed down in different farms, they stole, and bread or cheese or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
